    "directions": [
        "Bring water and rice to a boil in a saucepan",
        "Reduce heat to medium-low, cover, and simmer until the rice is tender and liquid has been absorbed, 20 to 25 minutes",
        "Combine rice, coconut milk, sugar, and salt in a pot; cook and stir until thickened and creamy, about 20 minutes",
        "Beat milk and egg together in a bowl",
        "Spoon 1 to 2 tablespoons rice mixture into milk mixture and beat to warm and temper milk mixture",
        "Slowly pour milk mixture into rice mixture while constantly beating; cook, stirring constantly, until pudding is heated through, 2 to 3 minutes",
        "Remove pot from heat and stir coconut oil, vanilla extract, and coconut extract into pudding; refrigerate until chilled, about 1 hour",
